data.description: Introducing the perfect oasis in the heart of East Austin! This incredible 3 bed, 2 bath home is an absolute gem, conveniently located just minutes from the breathtaking Walter E Long Lake. Step inside and discover a true chef's dream kitchen, complete with striking granite countertops and sleek stainless steel appliances. The primary suite is an absolute retreat, offering a spacious additional sitting area that's just waiting to be transformed into your dream home office or a cozy second living room. Imagine immersing yourself in a book or catching up on your favorite TV shows in this private sanctuary. This home has been meticulously cared for, with numerous upgrades throughout the years. Fresh interior and exterior paint, fresh new carpeting installed in May 2023, creating a luxurious and inviting atmosphere. The hallway bath received a stylish makeover in 2020, boasting a new vanity and sleek sliding shower door. In 2017, the kitchen was treated to beautiful new tile flooring, while the main areas received durable and stunning laminate floors. And to ensure your comfort year-round, ceiling fans have been installed in each bedroom. Step outside to the covered front and back porches, where you can sip your morning coffee or unwind with a glass of wine as you take in the serene views of your well-maintained yard. The neighborhood pool and playground offer the perfect setting for creating lasting memories with family and friends. Just minutes away, you'll find ABIA and Tesla Giga for all your travel and commuting needs. Downtown Austin is also within easy reach, so you can enjoy the vibrant city scene whenever you desire. The YMCA, Harvey Penick Golf Campus, and Morris Williams Golf Course are nearby for those seeking an active lifestyle, while East Austin caters to your every foodie whim with a plethora of restaurants, shops, and entertainment options.
